'''弗朗西斯·加里·鲍尔斯'''（{{lang-en|Francis Gary Powers}}，{{bd|1929年|8月17日|1977年|8月1日}}）是一名[[美国空軍|美国空軍]][[飞行员|飞行员]]。在驾驶[[中央情报局|中央情报局]][[U-2侦察机|U-2侦察机]]飞经[[苏联|苏联]][[领空|领空]]执行[[侦察|侦察]]任务时被击落，从而引发[[1960年U-2擊墜事件|1960年U-2擊墜事件]]。<!-- whose [[Central_Intelligence_Agency|Central Intelligence Agency]] [[Lockheed_U-2|U-2 spy plane]] was shot down while flying a [[reconnaissance|reconnaissance]] mission over Soviet Union [[airspace|airspace]], causing the [[1960_U-2_incident|1960 U-2 incident]].--><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foia.cia.gov/powers.asp |title=CIA FOIA - Francis Gary Powers: U-2 Spy Pilot Shot Down by the Soviets |publisher=Foia.cia.gov |date= |accessdate=2013-11-09 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120831191815/http://www.foia.cia.gov/powers.asp |archivedate=2012-08-31 }}</ref>

== 早期生活 ==
鲍尔斯出生在[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]][[詹金斯_(肯塔基州)|詹金斯]]，父母分别为奥利弗和艾达·鲍尔斯。他在州界另一边的弗吉尼亚[[庞德_(弗吉尼亚州)|庞德]]长大。1950年从[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]的{{link-en|密里根学院|Milligan College}}毕业之后，他成为了一名[[美国空军|美国空军]]少尉。在训练完结之后，鲍尔斯作为一名{{link-en|F-84|F-84 Thunderjet}}驾驶员被分配至[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]]{{link-en|透纳空军基地|Turner Air Force Base}}的{{link-en|第468战略战斗机中队|468th Strategic Fighter Squadron}}。据其子回忆，由于他在单引擎[[喷气式飞机|喷气式飞机]]上的出色成绩而被[[CIA|CIA]]征召。在[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]期间，他并没有执行过飞行任务<!--Powers was born in [[Jenkins,_Kentucky|Jenkins, Kentucky]], to Oliver and Ida Powers. He grew up in [[Pound,_Virginia|Pound, Virginia]], just across the state border. Graduating from [[Milligan_College|Milligan College]] in [[Tennessee|Tennessee]], in 1950, he was commissioned as a second lieutenant in the [[United_States_Air_Force|United States Air Force]]. After completing his training, Powers was assigned to the [[468th_Strategic_Fighter_Squadron|468th Strategic Fighter Squadron]] at [[Turner_Air_Force_Base|Turner Air Force Base]], [[Georgia_(U.S._state)|Georgia]], as an [[F-84_Thunderjet|F-84 Thunderjet]] pilot. According to his son, he did not fly combat missions during the [[Korean_War|Korean War]], because he was recruited by the [[CIA|CIA]] for his outstanding record in single engine [[jet_aircraft|jet aircraft]].--><ref name = "unattn">{{cite book |last= Powers |first= Francis Gary |coauthors= Curt Gentry |title= Operation Overflight |publisher= Hodder & Stoughton Ltd | isbn= 978-1-57488-422-7|language=en|date=May 1971}}</ref><!-- By 1960, Powers was already a veteran of many covert aerial reconnaissance missions.-->。

== U-2击坠事件 ==
{{Main|1960年U-2擊墜事件}}
